gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 109, Nets 98
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Nets, 109-98. Stephen Curry recorded 29 points, five rebounds and four 3PM for the Warriors, while Jonathan Kuminga added 28 points and 10 rebounds in the victory. Cam Thomas tallied 18 points and five rebounds for the Nets in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 22-25 on the season, while the Nets fall to 20-29.
